  "title": "Classic Faithful 32x",
  "description": "A double-resolution texture pack that continues Vattic’s original Faithful 32x32 pack with the classic textures.",
  "body": "<center>\n\t<img style=\"width: 1142px;\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/wordmarks/outlined/cracked/cf32_wordmark.png\">\n\t<h1>A double resolution texture pack that continues Vattic’s original Faithful 32x32 pack with the classic textures.</h1>\n</center>\n<p>\n\tCreated as a response to Faithful's changing art style, Classic Faithful 32x aims to preserve and restore Vattic's original “painted” art in its full glory. Most importantly, it also keeps the pack updated, remaking new textures to match the classic style as well.\n\t<br><br>\n\tClassic Faithful 32x goes all out on nostalgia! This pack features all the classic textures by Vattic himself. When applicable, textures from after his era have been made consistent with his art as well, oftentimes using complicated reverse-engineering processes to ensure the pack is as accurate as possible. Install this pack for a true blast from the past!\n  \n</p>\n<center>\n\t<a href=\"https://discord.gg/KSEhCVtg4J\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img style=\"width: 1142px;\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/discord_button.png\" alt=\"Discord Server\">\n\t</a>\n  <br><br>\n\t<a href=\"https://faithfulpack.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img style=\"width: 1142px;\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/website_button.png\" alt=\"Website\">\n\t</a>\n</center>\n<hr>\n<center><h2>Additional Information:</h2></center>\n<p>\n\tIf you have any feedback, want to report a bug, or generally need help,\n\tjoin our <a href=\"https://discord.gg/sN9YRQbBv7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Discord</a> server above, make a\n\t<a href=\"https://github.com/ClassicFaithful/32x-Programmer-Art/issues\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub issue</a>,\n\tor comment below. For any commercial or distribution-related questions, refer to our\n\t<a href=\"http://faithfulpack.net/license\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">license</a>.\n\t<br><br>\n\tAll textures and add-ons are provided by contributors volunteering in their free time.\n\tAnyone can submit textures through our Discord server linked above, or make an\n\t<a href=\"http://faithfulpack.net/addons\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">add-on</a>\n\tto officially list on our website. Before you begin, make sure to read our\n\t<a href=\"https://docs.faithfulpack.net/pages/textures/cf32-texturing-guidelines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">texturing guidelines</a>\n\twhich precisely outline the art style of the pack.\n\t<br><br>\n\tEach pack has listings on our <a href=\"faithfulpack.net\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">website</a>,\n\t<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/faithful_resource_pack/projects\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CurseForge</a>,\n\t<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/member/faithful_resource_pack/submissions/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Planet Minecraft</a>,\n\tand <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Faithful-Resource-Pack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Modrinth</a>,\n\tand some packs are additionally listed on <a href=\"https://mcpedl.com/user/faithful-resource-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MCPEDL</a>\n\tand the <a href=\"https://www.minecraftforum.net/members/Faithful_Resource_Pack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Minecraft Forums</a>.\n\t<strong>Downloads from any other sites are unofficial, unsupported and could be dangerous!</strong>\n\tRemember to stay safe on the internet.\n</p>\n<hr>\n<center><h2>Our Other Projects:</h2></center>\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">\n\t<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/faithful-32x\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img\n\t\t\tstyle=\"width: 1142px;\"\n\t\t\tsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/f32_button.png\"\n\t\t\talt=\"Faithful 32x\"\n\t\t>\n\t</a>\n\t<br><br>\n\t<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/faithful-64x\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img\n\t\t\tstyle=\"width: 1142px;\"\n\t\t\tsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/f64_button.png\"\n\t\t\talt=\"Faithful 64x\"\n\t\t>\n\t</a>\n    <br><br>\n\t<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/classic-faithful-32x-jappa\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img\n\t\t\tstyle=\"width: 1142px;\"\n\t\t\tsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/cf32j_button.png\"\n\t\t\talt=\"Classic Faithful 32x Jappa\"\n\t\t>\n\t</a>\n\t<br><br>\n\t<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/classic-faithful-64x\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img\n\t\t\tstyle=\"width: 1142px;\"\n\t\t\tsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/cf64j_button.png\"\n\t\t\talt=\"Classic Faithful 64x Jappa\"\n\t\t>\n\t</a>\n</div>",
